4 A BILL
5 TO BE ENTITLED
6 AN ACT
7
8
9 Relating to Henry County; to abolish the Southeast
10 Alabama Human Development Council; and to provide for the
11 transfer of the duties of the council.
12 BE IT ENACTED BY THE LEGISLATURE OF ALABAMA:
13 Section 1. (a) The Southeast Alabama Human Development
14 Council, established pursuant to Section 45-34-83, Code of
15 Alabama 1975, is abolished.
16 (b) Pursuant to the provisions of Chapter 1 of Title
17 44, Code of Alabama 1975, the Alabama Department of Youth
18 Services shall assume the duties of the council.
19 Section 2. Section 45-34-83, Code of Alabama 1975,
20 establishing the Southeast Alabama Human Development Council,
21 is repealed.
22 Section 3. This act shall become effective on June 1,
23 2026.
